<li><i>Becoming Ex-Muslim: The secret group for Aussies who've left their faith</i> (2017) – Patrick Abboud for <i><a href="/wiki/The_Feed_(Australian_TV_series)" title="The Feed (Australian TV series)">The Feed</a></i></li></ul>
</div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Books_by_ex-Muslims">Books by ex-Muslims</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Apostasy_in_Islam&amp;action=edit&amp;section=29" title="Edit section: Books by ex-Muslims">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
