<li id="cite_note-Gomaa-168"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Gomaa_168-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Gomaa_168-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Grand_Mufti" title="Grand Mufti">Grand Mufti</a> <a href="/wiki/Ali_Gomaa" title="Ali Gomaa">Ali Gomaa</a>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://newsweek.washingtonpost.com/onfaith/muslims_speak_out/2007/07/gomaas_statement_on_apostasy.html">Gomaa's Statement on Apostasy</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20081224161053/http://newsweek.washingtonpost.com/onfaith/muslims_speak_out/2007/07/gomaas_statement_on_apostasy.html">Archived</a> 24 December 2008 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Washington_Post" title="The Washington Post">The Washington Post</a></i>, 25 July 2007.</span>
